  "remarks": "Isle of Man-administered company that controls ship-owning companies in Hong Kong. The ships are operated by sanctioned Safiran Payam Darya Shipping Lines (SAPID) that took over IRISL’s bulk services and routes and uses vessels previously owned by IRISL. The Hong Kong companies are: Insight World Ltd, Kingdom New Ltd, Logistic Smart Ltd, Neuman Ltd and New Desire Ltd. Technical management of the vessels is carried out by sanctioned Soroush Saramin Asatir (SSA).",
